special_powers.name: MAGNOBALL CHAMPION
special_powers.description: Give Cosmic Boy a power action and he can use Telekinesis twice as a free action. When Cosmic Boy has two action tokens, he can use Telekinesis as a free action.

special_powers.name: ELECTED LEADER
special_powers.description: Cosmic Boy can use Leadership. When he does, all characters with the Legion of Super Heroes keyword are considered a lower point value.

special_powers.name: STRONGEST MIND
special_powers.description: Saturn Girl can use Mind Control and, if she has no action tokens, she can use it as a free action. When she uses Mind Control, she isn't dealt unavoidable damage from it and she increases her attack value by +1 for each action token assigned to her target.

special_powers.name: ARC LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Give Lightning Lad a power action and make a ranged combat attack against a single target using his printed damage value. Each time he hits, after actions resolve, he may then make a ranged combat attack as a free action against another single target as if he occupied the previously hit character's square, replacing his range value with his printed range value minus the number of hits he has made this turn with this power and also using his printed damage value.

special_powers.name: TACTICAL DEPLOYMENT
special_powers.description: When an opposing character within 8 squares is given a free action, if that character has been given a non-free action this turn, after actions resolve, deal that character 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: UNDER DARKSEID'S CONTROL
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Darkseid is on the map, modify Daxamite's attack value by +1 and Daxamite's defense value by -1.

special_powers.name: MAN OF VALOR
special_powers.description: Mon-El can use Defend and adjacent friendly characters modify their defense values by +1.

special_powers.name: SPLITTING BODIES
special_powers.description: When Triplicate Girl is adjacent to 2 or more friendly characters named Triplicate Girl and makes an attack roll, she may roll 3 dice instead of 2 and then choose 1 die to ignore. When Triplicate Girl is adjacent to 2 or more friendly characters named Triplicate Girl and an opposing character targets her with an attack, roll a d6 and decrease the opponent's attack total by the result.

special_powers.name: MORPH: SHRINKING VIOLET
special_powers.description: Give Shrinking Violet a move or close combat action that deals no pushing damage. After actions resolve replace her with any character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: SIZE CHANGE ATTACK
special_powers.description: Shrinking Violet can use Close Combat Expert. When she does after actions resolve she has "standard damage symbol" until your next turn.

special_powers.name: INTANGIBILITY AND DISRUPTION
special_powers.description: Phantom Girl can use Phasing/Teleport. When she uses Phasing/Teleport and passes through any squares occupied by characters holding an object, she may remove any of those objects from the game. When she uses Phasing/Teleport and passes through characters assigned any relics or resources, those characters can't use those relics or resources until your next turn.

special_powers.name: PHASING ATTACK
special_powers.description: Phantom Girl can use Incapacitate. When she is given a move action, after actions resolve, she may be given a close combat action as a free action, targeting any one opposing character occupying a square she moved through.

special_powers.name: BLIGHTED
special_powers.description: Blight can use Mind Control and Phasing/Teleport. When it uses Mind Control, modify its attack value by +1 for each adjacent friendly character with the Blight keyword.

special_powers.name: UNAFFECTED BY HEAT
special_powers.description: When Polar Boy or an adjacent friendly character is targeted by a ranged combat attack, the attacker can't use Energy Explosion.

special_powers.name: BLINDING SNOW
special_powers.description: Polar Boy can use Incapacitate. When he does, and hits a character with no action tokens, give that character 2 action tokens instead.

special_powers.name: ILLUSIONS SEEM REAL
special_powers.description: Sensor Girl can use Perplex, but only to modify an opposing character's attack or defense value.

special_powers.name: NOT WHERE YOU THINK
special_powers.description: Sensor Girl can use Probability Control and Shape Change.

special_powers.name: JUMP INTO A NEW BODY
special_powers.description: Daemonite can use Regeneration. At the beginning of your turn, Daemonite can use Regeneration as a free action, but subtracts 3 from the d6 instead of 2.

special_powers.name: DAEMONITE BIOLOGY
special_powers.description: Daemonite can use Shape Change. When Daemonite makes a successful Shape Change roll, it may use a standard attack power possessed by the character who originally targeted Daemonite until the end of your turn, even if that power is lost.

special_powers.name: SHOOTING CLAWS
special_powers.description: Timber Wolf has a range value of 6. Whenever he hits with an attack, you may roll a d6. If you do, Timber Wolf's damage value becomes the result and is locked until the attack resolves.

special_powers.name: HEALING FACTOR
special_powers.description: Timber Wolf can use Regeneration. He can use it normally, or he can use it as a free action if he's been given a close combat action this turn.

special_powers.name: SHE KEEPS GETTING BIGGER!
special_powers.description: When Giganta uses the Giant Reach ability and makes a close combat attack, all squares within a range of her click number minus 1 and line of fire are considered adjacent.

special_powers.name: HATRED FOR MY PREY
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Cheetah a free action and choose an opposing character. As long as that character is on the map, Cheetah modifies her combat values except range by +1. If that character is named Wonder Woman, Cheetah can use Exploit Weakness.

special_powers.name: WE'VE DANCED THIS DANCE BEFORE
special_powers.description: Cheetah can use Combat Reflexes. If Cheetah has no action tokens, she can use Exploit Weakness.

special_powers.name: POUNCE MY PREY
special_powers.description: Cheetah can use Leap/Climb. When Cheetah resolves a move action, you may give her a close combat action as a free action.

special_powers.name: PRESSING MY ADVANTAGE
special_powers.description: Cheetah can use Outwit, but only to target characters that have two action tokens.

special_powers.name: ONE...
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose one to last until you choose for this power again. Ultra-Boy can use Running Shot, or he can use Charge.

special_powers.name: ...POWER
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose one to last until you choose for this power again. Ultra-Boy can use Penetrating Psychic Blast, or he can use Energy Explosion, or he can use Super Strength.

special_powers.name: ...AT A TIME
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose one to last until you choose for this power again. Ultra-Boy can use Impervious, or he can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: GEMWORLD PORTAL
special_powers.description: Once per game, when Amethyst hits an opposing character, you may choose that neither character may make a ranged combat attack and she and that character may only target each other with close combat attacks until one of them is KO'd.

special_powers.name: FOR MY LOVE
special_powers.description: When Blok is adjacent to a friendly character named White Witch or Black Witch, that character can use Mastermind, but only to transfer damage to Blok, regardless of his point value.

special_powers.name: OUT OF THE WAY
special_powers.description: Blok can use Charge and Quake. When he uses Charge, he can use Improved Movement: Destroy Blocking, Characters.

special_powers.name: ENERGY ABSORPTION
special_powers.description: Blok can use Invulnerability. When Blok is targeted by a ranged combat attack, he can use Impervious instead.

special_powers.name: FOR DAWNSTAR
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Dawnstar has taken damage from an attack since your last turn, modify Wildfire's attack and damage values by +1 if he targets a character that hit Dawnstar since your last turn.

special_powers.name: THIS BATTLE ENDS HERE!
special_powers.description: Wildfire can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Pulse Wave. He can use Pulse Wave normally, or you may give him a double power action to use it and his printed damage value is dealt to all hit characters.

special_powers.name: ENERGY REFORMING
special_powers.description: When this click is revealed, stop turning the dial. Wildfire can use Impervious and Regeneration. When he uses Regeneration, either the minimum result is 1 or he can use it as a free action and subtracts 3 from the d6 roll instead of 2.

special_powers.name: TELEPORT DISKS
special_powers.description: Gates can use Phasing/Teleport. Gates can carry up to four friendly characters, regardless of their speed symbols. If all carried characters share a keyword with him, don't modify his speed value from the Carry ability.

special_powers.name: INSTANTANEOUS SHIFT
special_powers.description: Gates can use Super Senses, but succeeds on a result of 4 - 6.

special_powers.name: MOLECULAR SIGHT
special_powers.description: Mr. Majestic ignores Shape Change. When Mr. Majestic uses the Move and Attack ability, he modifies his attack value by -1 instead of -2.

special_powers.name: SMARTER THAN ALL OF YOU COMBINED
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor's powers can't be countered. Adjacent friendly characters with a lower point value have "Superman Enemy team ability symbol".

special_powers.name: IF YOU WANT A JOB DONE RIGHT
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor has "wing symbol" and can use Invulnerability and Running Shot.

special_powers.name: ANTI-MATTER TOUCH
special_powers.description: Mano can use Poison. He can use it normally, or he can deal damage to only 1 opposing character and that damage is penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: DISINTEGRATE WALLS
special_powers.description: Give Mano a free action and destroy an adjacent wall or square of blocking terrain.

special_powers.name: GREATEST ESCAPE ARTIST OF THREE WORLDS
special_powers.description: When Mister Miracle would be hit by an attack, if you give him an action token he evades the attack instead.

special_powers.name: FREETHINKER OF APOKOLIPS
special_powers.description: Mister Miracle can use Outwit and Shape Change. Mister Miracle can use Empower, but only to modify the damage value of a friendly character named Big Barda.

special_powers.name: DEFEATING YOU WILL PROVE MY WORTH TO FATHER
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Kalibak a double power action. Place him adjacent to an opposing character with a higher point value and he may make a close combat attack targeting that character as a free action.

special_powers.name: I AM THE ONE TRUE SON OF DARKSEID
special_powers.description: If a character named Darkseid or Orion is on the map, modify Kalibak's attack value by +1 and his defense value by -1.

special_powers.name: RADIANT BURST
special_powers.description: When Lightray is KO'd, before removing him from the game, make a ranged combat attack with an attack value of 10 that can't be rerolled. The area of effect for this attack is all characters within 5 squares, and each hit character is dealt 3 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: INFECTIOUS OPTIMISM
special_powers.description: Lightray can use Perplex, but only to target friendly characters.

special_powers.name: CYBORG LEADER
special_powers.description: Tharok can use Leadership. When he does, characters with the Fatal Five keyword are considered a lower point value.

special_powers.name: ARM CONFIGURATIONS
special_powers.description: Tharok can use Blades/Claws/Fangs, Energy Explosion, and Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: INTERSTELLAR TRACKING
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose an opposing character within 10 squares. Lines of fire drawn to that character this turn are only blocked by blocking terrain.

special_powers.name: DURLAN PHYSIOLOGY
special_powers.description: Chameleon Girl can use Shape Change and Stealth. At the beginning of your turn, give Chameleon Girl a free action and choose one from "boot symbol", "wing symbol", "dolphin symbol" and also choose one from "tiny symbol", "standard damage symbol", "giant symbol". Chameleon Girl has the chosen symbols until you choose again.

special_powers.name: DIFFERENT CREATURES
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose one: Chameleon Girl can use Incapacitate and Poison, she can use Combat Reflexes and Exploit Weakness, or she can use Flurry and Sidestep.

special_powers.name: SIZE CHANGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, give Colossal Boy a free action and chose from "standard damage symbol", "giant damage symbol" or "colossal damage symbol". He has the chosen symbol until your next turn. When he has "colossal damage symbol", he can use Impervious when targeted by ranged combat attacks.

special_powers.name: YOU HARMED YERA
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Chameleon Girl has taken damage since your last turn Colossal Boy can use Battle Fury, Charge, and Improved Movement: Hindering, Destroy Blocking, Characters. When he uses Charge in this way, he can use it as a free action, he doesn't halve his speed value from it, and may only target opposing characters that hit Chameleon Girl last turn.

special_powers.name: TEACHER AND STUDENT
special_powers.description: When Stargirl is 110 points, adjacent friendly characters with a shared keyword and a lower point value modify their attack values by +1. When Stargirl is 75 points and is adjacent to a friendly character with a shared keyword and a higher point value, modify her attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: COSMIC BELT OR COSMIC ROD
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, roll a d6 and Stargirl can use the indicated effects until your next turn: 1-2: Stargirl has a range value of 4 "two targets" and can use Combat Reflexes, Incapacitate, and the Sharpshooter ability. 3-4: Stargirl can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Ranged Combat Expert. 5-6: Stargirl chooses either result above.

special_powers.name: STUNNING BLOW
special_powers.description: When Stargirl uses Incapacitate, after actions resolve, deal her printed damage divided any way you choose among the hit characters.

special_powers.name: STAR PUPIL
special_powers.description: Give Stargirl a free action and choose a standard attack or damage power that can be used by an adjacent friendly character with a higher point value and a shared keyword. Stargirl can use the choosen power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: POP CULTURE COLLECTOR
special_powers.description: After objects have been placed, you may place any 2 objects in each other's squares. Starman modifies his relic rolls by +1.

special_powers.name: STAR ROD AND JUJITSU
special_powers.description: Starman can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Super Senses. When he is targeted with a close combat attack and either evades it or it misses, give the attacker an action token after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: ABSOLUTE DARKNESS
special_powers.description: Shadow Lass can use Smoke Cloud. Friendly characters that only occupy squares with these markers can't have lines of fire drawn to them, and opposing characters that only occupy squares with these markers can't draw lines of fire.

special_powers.name: FROM SORCERER'S WORLD
special_powers.description: Glorith can use Super Senses. Glorith can copy a second team ability, if it is possessed by a character with the Mystical keyword.

special_powers.name: TEMPORAL SHIELDING
special_powers.description: Glorith can use Barrier. If Glorith is adjacent to a blocking terrain marker she placed, she can use Toughness.

special_powers.name: TIME MANIPULATION
special_powers.description: Glorith can use Perplex and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: RIDDLE ME THIS, BATMAN!
special_powers.description: The Riddler can use Perplex regardless of range and line of fire, but can only target opposing characters.

special_powers.name: PHOTOGRAPHIC MEMORY
special_powers.description: Edward Nigma ignores hindering terrain when drawing lines of fire to characters who didn't move during their last turn.

special_powers.name: HIDDEN CLUES
special_powers.description: Edward Nigma can use Mind Control and Shape Change. When he uses Mind Control, after actions resolve, hit characters are given up to 2 action tokens that don't deal pushing damage.

special_powers.name: I KNOW YOUR SECRET, MR. WAYNE
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within line of fire can't use Shape Change, the Alter Ego, or Morph powers or abilities.

special_powers.name: TECHNOLOGY AND PATIENCE
special_powers.description: Black Manta can use the Carry ability. Lines of fire drawn to Black Manta by opposing characters are blocked if they cross water terrain.

special_powers.name: ME AM NOT BIZARRO!
special_powers.description: Bizarro costs 25 points for each Orrazib token you place on his card, up to 6 tokens. When Bizarro takes damage, remove one Orrazib token from his card. When Bizarro is healed through the use of Support, add one Orrazib token to his card (no more than the initial amount). When there are no Orrazib tokens on this card, KO Bizarro. At the beginning of your turn, roll a d6 and click Bizarro that many times. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: EMERALD EYE OF EKRON
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, place an Emerald Eye of Ekron relic token in Emerald Empress's square. This object doesn't count towards your force and is described on the back of this card. Emerald Empress automatically succeeds when rolling for the Emerald Eye of Ekron. When Emerald Empress is assigned the Emerald Eye of Ekron and has two action tokens, she can use her speed powers as a free action.

This character can use Mind Control, Incapacitate, Improved Targeting: Hindering, Characters, and isn't dealt unavoidable damage from Mind Control. When this character takes damage from an attack, Emerald Eye of Ekron is placed in an adjacent square. Characters may attempt to be assigned Emerald Eye of Ekron more than once per game.

special_powers.name: HYPNOSIS
special_powers.description: Universo can use Mind Control as if he had "3 targets". When he does, increase his attack value by the number of targets and, after actions resolve, heal him of 1 damage for each character with the Legion of Super Heroes keyword he hit with that attack.

special_powers.name: I'VE LEARNED A FEW THINGS
special_powers.description: Universo can use Incapacitate. When he does, after actions resolve he can use Smoke Cloud as a free action.

special_powers.name: MASTER OF MISDIRECTION
special_powers.description: Universo can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: HIGH LORD OF ALL DAEMONITES
special_powers.description: Helspont can use Leadership. When he does, treat all characters named Daemonite within 5 squares as if they were adjacent.

special_powers.name: IMMORTAL POWER
special_powers.description: Helspont can use Shape Change. When Helspont makes a successful Shape Change roll, immediately heal him of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: I INFILTRATED YOU LONG AGO
special_powers.description: Give Helspont a double power action and select an opposing character of a lower point value. Place Helspont and the chosen character in each other's squares, and after actions resolve, Helspont may be given a close or ranged combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: SMARTER THAN LORD EMP
special_powers.description: Helspont can use Outwit and Perplex. When he does, if he targets a character with the WildC.A.T.s keyword, he can use that power a second time this turn.

special_powers.name: PING! PING! PING!
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, if Orion has any action tokens, you may give him a free action and heal him of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: WE ARE AT WAR
special_powers.description: When Orion targets a character with the Apokalips keyword, modify his attack value by +1. When he targets a character named Darkseid, modify his damage value by +1 and ignore any defense powers the target can use.

special_powers.name: ASTRO-HARNESS
special_powers.description: Orion can use Phasing/Teleport, Running Shot, and the Flight ability.

special_powers.name: DOG OF WAR
special_powers.description: Orion can use Exploit Weakness and Flurry.

special_powers.name: FOR DARKSEID!
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Apokolips keyword and not named Darkseid modify their attack and damage values by +1 when they have one action token.

special_powers.name: LORD OF APOKOLIPS
special_powers.description: When Darkseid is dealt penetrating damage, it can be reduced. If Darkseid didn't use Outwit during your last turn, his powers can't be countered.

special_powers.name: BOOM TUBE TECHNOLOGY
special_powers.description: If Darkseid has no action tokens, he can use Running Shot and Improved Movement: Characters. If he has one action token, he can use Phasing/Teleport, and when he does, he may be given a ranged combat attack as a free action after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: BOW BEFORE DARKSEID
special_powers.description: Darkseid can use Outwit and Leadership. When he uses Leadership, he may remove 2 action tokens from an adjacent friendly character instead of 1 and if he does, that character is dealt 1 unavoidable damage at the end of the turn.

special_powers.name: TAPPED INTO EVERY COMPUTER ON EARTH
special_powers.description: Give Computo a free action and choose an opposing character within 8 squares. The chosen character must be holding an object, be within 1 square of an object, or be assigned a relic or resource. Place an ID token on the chosen character's card. When Computo uses Outwit or Perplex, he may target characters with an ID token anywhere on the map.

special_powers.name: LARGE ROBOTIC ARMS
special_powers.description: Computo can use Flurry, Precision Strike, and Quake.

special_powers.name: PROGRAMMED TO HELP
special_powers.description: Computo can use the Legion of Super Heroes team ability. Computo ignores damage dealt to him and is dealt 1 unavoidable damage instead. This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: THE INSPIRATION OF THE 31ST CENTURY
special_powers.description: Superboy can use Leadership and Super Strength. Friendly adjacent characters with a lower point value can use Willpower.

special_powers.name: PUNCH YOU BEFORE YOU SEE IT COMING
special_powers.description: Superboy can use Force Blast and Hypersonic Speed. When he uses Hypersonic Speed, he can only make close combat attacks.

special_powers.name: MAGICKS RESISTANCE
special_powers.description: White Witch ignores the Mystics team ability.

special_powers.name: BATTLEFIELD PROMOTION: AUFERO MAGUS INFUSCO!
special_powers.description: When White Witch damages one or more opposing characters with the Mystical keyword or assigned a resource, after actions resolve place a Promotion Token on her character card. You may then roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and add 1 for each Promotion Token on her character card; on a result of 7 or higher, replace this character with SLOSH #047b on the same click number.

special_powers.name: MYSTICAL ENERGY
special_powers.description: During your turn choose one: Give White Witch a power action, and each opposing character's combat values can't be modified until your next turn; or give White Witch a free action, and each opposing character can't be given more than one free action until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SHIELDING MAGICKS
special_powers.description: White Witch can use Barrier, Energy Shield/Deflection and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: SORCERER'S WORLD
special_powers.description: After objects are placed, Black Witch may exchange any standard objects that are 5 or more squares from her starting area with distinct relics from outside the game totaling no more than 20 points.

special_powers.name: FOR US, MY LOVE
special_powers.description: Black Witch can use Defend. Friendly characters named Blok modify their defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: DARK MAGICKS
special_powers.description: Black Witch can use Steal Energy. When Black Witch attacks an opposing character with the Mystical keyword, she can use Steal Energy with ranged combat attacks.

special_powers.name: LINK TELEPATHICALLY
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Legion of Superheroes keyword within 4 squares can draw lines of fire and count range and squares from the square of any one friendly character within 4 squares of Tellus.

special_powers.name: TELEKINETIC SHIELD
special_powers.description: Tellus can use Energy Shield/Deflection, Super Senses, and Toughness.

special_powers.name: IMMORTAL PLANT ELEMENT
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn you may give Solomon Grundy a free action and heal him of 1 damage if he occupies printed hindering or water terrain.

special_powers.name: THE END OF SOLOMON GRUNDY
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, place 3 Resurrection tokens on Solomon Grundy's card. Solomon Grundy places 1 Resurrection token on his character card each time he hits an opposing character. When Solomon Grundy would be KO'd and has at least one Resurrection token on his card, instead click him to click #9, heal him of 1 damage for each Resurrection token on his card and remove all Resurrection tokens from his card. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: GENTLE MIND OR RAGING BEAST?
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game and when Solomon Grundy would be KO'd, choose one to last until he chooses again: he can use Outwit, or he can use Battle Fury and modifies his damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: NEVER REALLY THE END
special_powers.description: Solomon Grundy can use Regeneration.

special_powers.name: I LOVE MY TOYS!
special_powers.description: Characters with the "teddy bear" icon are Toys. Toyman may begin the game with 1 Toy attached to his base at no additional cost. Toyman increases his defense value by 1 for each Toy attached. Toyman can have up to 2 Toys attached.

special_powers.name: POWER BOOST
special_powers.description: Toyman can use Perplex. He can use it normally, or he can use it as a power action to modify the same combat value except damage of all friendly Toys on the map.

special_powers.name: CONDUIT OF THE SOURCE
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Takion a free action and choose: Perplex or Probability Control. Opposing characters can't target Takion with the chosen power this game.

special_powers.name: FASTER THAN THOUGHT
special_powers.description: Takion can use Hypersonic Speed and Pulse Wave. When he uses Hypersonic Speed he can use Pulse Wave instead of a ranged combat attack.

special_powers.name: MANIPULATING ENERGY
special_powers.description: Takion can use Probability Control. When Takion is hit with a ranged combat attack, he may immediately place a blocking terrain marker in an adjacent square; that marker remains on the map until destroyed or your next turn, even if this power is lost.

special_powers.name: THE PACT
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, you may announce a pact. If you do, the highest point character on your force and the highest point character on your opponent's force (300 points or less) can't target opposing characters with an attack until one of them has taken damage from an attack or, they are the only 2 characters on the map, or your opponent only has one character on the map. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: GENESIS REBORN
special_powers.description: Give Highfather a power action and replace him with SLOSH #051 Takion on the same click number.

special_powers.name: IZAYA, THE CREATOR
special_powers.description: Highfather can use Leadership, Probability Control, and Support. When he uses Support, the target's combat values are modified by +1 until the end of your next turn.

special_powers.name: WE'VE LEARNED TO SURVIVE
special_powers.description: If Big Barda and Mister Miracle have taken damage from a close combat attack, modify their defense value by +1 when they are targeted with a close combat attack this turn. If Big Barda and Mister Miracle have taken damage from a ranged combat attack, modify their defense value by +1 when they are targeted with a ranged combat attack this turn.

special_powers.name: POWER COUPLE
special_powers.description: If Big Barda and Mister Miracle are on the map through the Merge ability, give Big Barda and Mister Miracle a free action and choose any trait ability that the original characters could use. They can use that trait this turn, and the trait can't be chosen more than once per game.

special_powers.name: YOU'LL NEVER SLOW ME DOWN
special_powers.description: Big Barda and Mister Miracle can use Invulnerability and Super Senses.

special_powers.name: HIS PEACE AND HER RAGE
special_powers.description: Big Barda and Mister Miracle can use Close Combat Expert and Probability Control. If Big Barda and Mister Miracle didn't attack a character last turn, they can use Shape Change.

special_powers.name: ATOMIC AXE
special_powers.description: Persuader can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Combat Reflexes. When he rolls a d6 for Blades/Claws/Fangs and the result is 3 or less, he deals penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: CUT THROUGH ANYTHING
special_powers.description: Persuader can use Precision Strike and Quake.

special_powers.name: MONSTROUS BODY
special_powers.description: Validus can use Super Strength and can't be targeted by Penetrating/Psychic Blast. At the beginning of your turn, roll a d6, and on a result of 4-6, Validus can immediately use Pulse Wave as a free action with a locked damage value of 2, ignoring friendly characters.

special_powers.name: BRAIN BOLTS
special_powers.description: Validus can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When an opposing character with an action token takes damage from Validus's attack, give that character an action token.

special_powers.name: MORPH: CHANGE SIZE
special_powers.description: Give Mordru a power action, or when he takes damage from an opponent's attack, you may replace him with SLOSH #101 Mordru on the same click number.

special_powers.name: MYSTICAL RELICS
special_powers.description: When Mordru makes a relic roll, modify the result +2. Once per game give Mordru a double power action and place a relic 15 points or less from outside of the game in his square.

special_powers.name: LIMILESS MAGIC
special_powers.description: Give Mordru a free action and choose a standard attack power. Mordru can use that power until the beginning of your next turn.

special_powers.name: MOLECULAR MAGIC
special_powers.description: Mordru can use Invincible. Give Mordru a free action if he has two action tokens and place a standard light object from outside the game in his square.

special_powers.name: LORD OF CHAOS
special_powers.description: Mordru can use Probability Control. Opposing characters within range and line of fire can't use Probability Control or the Mystics team ability.

special_powers.name: THE GROWING DARKNESS

When this character is given a second action token, and actions resolve, choose a power that was not chosen last time: Perplex, Phasing/Teleport, Probability Control, Pulse Wave, or Regeneration and this character can use the chosen power until a new power is chosen.
